[{"id": 597438, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5178, "text": "G\u00f6klerde ne var, yerde ne varsa hepsi melik (k\u00e2inat\u0131n ger\u00e7ek h\u00fck\u00fcmdar\u0131), kudd\u00fbs (\u00e7ok y\u00fcce, her noksandan m\u00fcnezzeh) az\u00eez ve hak\u00eem olan Allah'\u0131 tesbih ve tenzih eder."}, {"id": 597439, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5179, "text": "O, \u00fcmm\u00eeler aras\u0131ndan, kendilerinden olan bir el\u00e7i g\u00f6nderdi. Bu el\u00e7i onlara Allah'\u0131n \u00e2yetlerini okur, onlar\u0131 ar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131r, onlara kitab\u0131 ve hikmeti \u00f6\u011fretir. Halbuki daha \u00f6nce belli ve kesin bir sap\u0131kl\u0131k i\u00e7inde idiler."}, {"id": 597440, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5180, "text": "Bu Peygamber, hen\u00fcz kendilerine kat\u0131lmam\u0131\u015f bulunan di\u011fer insanlara da g\u00f6nderilmi\u015ftir. O ger\u00e7ekten az\u00eezdir, hak\u00eemdir (\u00fcst\u00fcn kudret, tam h\u00fck\u00fcm ve hikmet sahibidir). [17,44; 3,20; 43,44; 26,214; 7,158; 6,19]"}, {"id": 597441, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5181, "text": "Bu, Allah'\u0131n l\u00fctfu olup onu diledi\u011fine verir. Allah b\u00fcy\u00fck l\u00fctuf ve ihsan sahibidir."}, {"id": 597442, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5182, "text": "Tevrat\u0131n mesaj\u0131n\u0131 ula\u015ft\u0131rma ve onu uygulama y\u00fck\u00fcml\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fcn\u00fc kabul ettikleri halde, sonra bu y\u00fck\u00fcml\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc yerine getirmeyenler, t\u0131pk\u0131 ciltlerle kitap ta\u015f\u0131yan merkebe benzer. Allah'\u0131n \u00e2yetlerini yalan sayan kimselerin d\u00fc\u015ft\u00fckleri durum ne fec\u00ee! Allah b\u00f6ylesi zalim g\u00fcr\u00fbhu hid\u00e2yet etmez, emellerine ula\u015ft\u0131rmaz. [7,179]"}, {"id": 597443, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5183, "text": "De ki: \u201cEy kendilerine Yahudi diyenler! \u0130nsanlar aras\u0131nda yaln\u0131z kendinizin Allah'\u0131n dostlar\u0131 oldu\u011funu iddia etti\u011finize g\u00f6re, bu iddian\u0131zda tutarl\u0131 iseniz, haydi hemen \u00f6lmeyi temenni edin de bir an \u00f6nce O\u2019na kavu\u015fun. [2,94-96]"}, {"id": 597444, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5184, "text": "Ama onlar bizzat yapt\u0131klar\u0131 zul\u00fcmler sebebiyle asla \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fc temenni etmezler. Allah o zalimleri pek iyi bilir."}, {"id": 597445, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5185, "text": "De ki: \u201cSizin ka\u00e7t\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z o \u00f6l\u00fcm var ya, o mutlaka sizi kar\u015f\u0131layacakt\u0131r. Sonra da g\u00f6r\u00fcnmeyen ve g\u00f6r\u00fcnen ne varsa hepsini bilen Allah'\u0131n huzuruna g\u00f6t\u00fcr\u00fcleceksiniz, O da sizin yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 tek tek bildirecek (ve ondan \u00f6t\u00fcr\u00fc kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 verecektir). [4,78]"}, {"id": 597446, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 487, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5186, "text": "Ey iman edenler! Cuma namaz\u0131na ezan ile \u00e7a\u011f\u0131r\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z zaman derhal Allah'\u0131 zikretmeye (hutbe ve namaza) gidin, al\u0131\u015fveri\u015fi b\u0131rak\u0131n. E\u011fer bilirseniz, bu sizin i\u00e7in \u00e7ok hay\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r. [17,19]"}, {"id": 597447, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 487, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5187, "text": "Namaz tamamlan\u0131nca yery\u00fcz\u00fcne yay\u0131l\u0131n, i\u015finize g\u00fcc\u00fcn\u00fcze gidin, Allah'\u0131n l\u00fctfundan nasibinizi aray\u0131n. Felaha ermenizi \u00fcmid ederek Allah\u2019\u0131 \u00e7ok zikrediniz."}, {"id": 597428, "identifier": "tr.yildirim", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 487, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Suat Y\u0131ld\u0131r\u0131m", "transelator_en_name": "Suat Yildirim", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5188, "text": "Onlar bir ticaret veya bir e\u011flence g\u00f6r\u00fcnce oraya do\u011fru s\u00f6k\u00fcn edip, seni hutbe verirken ayakta b\u0131rak\u0131verdiler. De ki: Allah'\u0131n nezdinde \u00e2hirette olan nasip, buradaki e\u011flenceden ve ticaretten elbette daha hay\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r. Allah r\u0131z\u0131k verenlerin en hay\u0131rl\u0131s\u0131d\u0131r. {KM, Matta 6,26}"}]